Package com.github.upthewaterspout.fates.core.states

This package contains all logic related to executing tests multiple times to explore an unknown space of possible test states.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Decider
    Interface for making a choice between a set of possible options See StateExplorationHarness for how to use this interface.
    RepeatedTest
    A test which contains decision points and should be run many times to explore different possible decisions and their affects.
    StateExplorer
    An algorithm for exploring the space of possible decisions during a test run.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    StateExplorationHarness
    A testing harness for running tests many times, exploring the affects of different decisions on the test.

Package com.github.upthewaterspout.fates.core.states Description

This package contains all logic related to executing tests multiple times to explore an unknown space of possible test states. See StateExplorationHarness for where to start.
